## **ğŸ“Œ Key Advantages Over JSON/YAML/XML**
âœ… **No Ambiguity** â€“ Strict typing (no `yes`/`no` vs `true`/`false` like YAML)  
âœ… **Built-in Schema Validation** â€“ No need for external schemas  
âœ… **Supports Comments** â€“ Unlike JSON  
âœ… **Cleaner Than XML** â€“ No closing tags or `< >` clutter  
âœ… **Secure** â€“ No arbitrary code execution (unlike YAML)  
âœ… **Future-Ready** â€“ Designed for payments, APIs, and more  

